text: I had an old mac that I wanted to sell, researched several different sites and asked for Quote: s. GoRoostr was the only one to give me a Quote: and have a shipping label available the same day. Their website was easy to use and the shipping process was simple. They let me know when they received my item, and also notified me when my item has been inspected and if the Quote: d amount had changed. Overall had a wonderful experience with GoRoostr and will be using their services in the future if needed.
